 ggml/src/ggml-sycl/CMakeLists.txt |  5 ++
 ggml/src/ggml-sycl/ggml-sycl.cpp  | 82 ++++++++++++++++++-------------
 3 files changed, 54 insertions(+), 34 deletions(-)

